<div class="es-pane" id="liveNoMatchScreen" hidden aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">We cannot confirm this is you</h1>
      <p>This is because your image does not match the photo we have on your file.</p>
      <p class="govuk-!-font-weight-bold">You can try to verify your identity again</p>
      <p>Make sure:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>your face is in the frame</li>
        <li>you are in a well lit area</li>
        <li>you are in front of a plain background</li>
        <li>you are not wearing a hat or sunglasses</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        If you are struggling to confirm your identity, you can still submit your check in. Your probation officer
        will confirm this is you when they review your check in.
      </p>
      <div class="govuk-button-group">
        <a class="govuk-button" role="button" data-liveness-retry>Verify identity again</a>
        <a
          class="govuk-button govuk-button--secondary"
          role="button"
          data-module="govuk-button"
          href="/{{ submissionId }}/check-your-answers"
        >
          Continue to check your answers
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
